# Emergent agent (E1) tracking artifacts. Their sandbox auto-commits
# `.emergent/emergent.yml` (job_id + timestamp) and a repo-level
# `.gitconfig` (sets user.name=emergent-agent-e1) into the working
# tree before push — both are sandbox-local metadata that has no
# business being in this repo. Ignore so they stop landing on master.
.emergent/
.gitconfig
